title: Dominican Republic CPI Transportation
description: The transportation sub-index of the CPI basket in Dominican Republic increased to 130.22 points in October of 2022 from 130 points in September of 2022. CPI Transportation in Dominican Republic averaged 70.54 points from 1999 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 130.53 points in August of 2022 and a record low of 14.17 points in February of 1999. This page provides - Dominican Republic Cpi Transportation- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of Dominican Republic
